        <TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Right" Margin="0,0,5,0" Foreground="White" VerticalAlignment="Center">
            Please help support Gallifrey <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&amp;hosted_button_id=G3MWL8E6UG4RS" Foreground="Black" RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">click to donate</Hyperlink>
